content.test_ScreenshotBrowser_Dual:
Item { // ScreenshotBrowser
    id: component
    width: 640
    height: 480
    
    
    
    state: "DualMode"

    ColumnLayout {
        id: dualImage
        width: 640
        height: 480
        implicitHeight: 460
        implicitWidth: 640

        Row {
            width: 640
            height: 21
            implicitHeight: 20
            implicitWidth: 240

            FocusScope { // RadioButton
                id: sideBySideButton
                activeFocusOnPress: false
                activeFocusOnTab: true
                checked: true
                hovered: false
                pressed: false
                text: "Side by Side"
                tooltip: ""
            }

            FocusScope { // RadioButton
                id: overlappedButton
                x: 120
                activeFocusOnPress: false
                activeFocusOnTab: true
                checked: false
                hovered: false
                pressed: false
                text: "Overlapped"
                tooltip: ""
            }
        }

        Item {
            y: 26
            width: 640
            height: 454
            implicitHeight: 435
            implicitWidth: 640

            RowLayout {
                id: sideBySideView
                width: 640
                height: 454
                implicitHeight: 435
                implicitWidth: 640

                Item {
                    width: 318
                    height: 454
                    implicitHeight: 435
                    implicitWidth: 318

                    Item { // ScaleToFitImage
                        x: 4
                        y: 4
                        width: 310
                        height: 446
                        imageHeight: 240
                        imageWidth: 160
                        
                        sourceSize: Qt.size(160,240)

                        Image {
                            id: image
                            x: 75
                            y: 103
                            width: 160
                            height: 240
                            implicitHeight: 240
                            implicitWidth: 160
                            progress: 1
                            
                            sourceSize: Qt.size(160,240)
                        }
                    }
                }

                Item {
                    x: 323
                    width: 317
                    height: 454
                    implicitHeight: 435
                    implicitWidth: 317

                    Item { // ScaleToFitImage
                        x: 4
                        y: 4
                        width: 309
                        height: 446
                        imageHeight: 240
                        imageWidth: 320
                        
                        sourceSize: Qt.size(320,240)

                        Image {
                            id: image
                            x: -5
                            y: 103
                            width: 320
                            height: 240
                            implicitHeight: 240
                            implicitWidth: 320
                            progress: 1
                            scale: 0.97
                            
                            sourceSize: Qt.size(320,240)
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
}
